TITLE: Scanning and displaying all data in an Accumulo table
DESCRIPTION: Creates a Scanner to read all entries from the 'GothamPD' table with empty authorizations and prints each key-value pair. The Scanner implements Iterable for convenient traversal.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/accumulo-website/blob/main/tour/data-model-code.md#2025-04-11_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
try (ScannerBase scan = client.createScanner("GothamPD", Authorizations.EMPTY)) {
  System.out.println("Gotham Police Department Persons of Interest:");
  for (Map.Entry<Key, Value> entry : scan) {
    System.out.printf("Key : %-50s  Value : %s\n", entry.getKey(), entry.getValue());
  }
}
```

