TITLE: Configuring Durability for BatchWriter
DESCRIPTION: Sets custom durability settings for a BatchWriter. This example shows how to configure NONE durability which provides no persistence guarantees but maximizes write performance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/accumulo-website/blob/main/_docs-2/getting-started/clients.md#2025-04-11_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
