TITLE: Reading Data Using Accumulo Scanner
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to configure and use a Scanner to read data from Accumulo with specific authorizations, ranges, and column families.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/accumulo-website/blob/main/1.3/user_manual/Writing_Accumulo_Clients.md#2025-04-11_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
// specify which visibilities we are allowed to see
