| <a name="gc_threads_delete" class="prop"></a> gc.threads.delete | **Available since:** 1.3.5<br>The number of threads used to delete RFiles and write-ahead logs.<br>**type:** COUNT, **zk mutable:** yes, **default value:** `16` |
