TITLE: Using DelegationTokens in MapReduce Job with Accumulo
DESCRIPTION: This Java code snippet demonstrates how to obtain a DelegationToken from Accumulo using a KerberosToken, and then use it to configure AccumuloInputFormat and AccumuloOutputFormat for a MapReduce job.
